1
00:00:00,270 --> 00:00:01,270
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,270 --> 00:00:02,370
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:02,370 --> 00:00:03,380
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:04,910 --> 00:00:06,210
(Episode 73)

5
00:00:08,210 --> 00:00:09,280
Tell me the truth.

6
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:12,820
Is Chairman Park Tae Ho really...

7
00:00:14,950 --> 00:00:15,950
my father?

8
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:18,760
Whose son am I?

9
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:23,160
Tell me who my father is!

10
00:00:25,100 --> 00:00:26,770
You're Park Tae Ho's son.

11
00:00:28,230 --> 00:00:32,000
You're Park Tae Ho's son.
Not even death can change that.

12
00:00:36,340 --> 00:00:37,340
Mom.

13
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,450
You had that same look
on your face...

14
00:00:40,510 --> 00:00:42,050
when you lied
about not killing anyone.

15
00:00:42,980 --> 00:00:45,050
I can see
right through your lies now.

16
00:00:47,090 --> 00:00:48,090
Hyun Jun.

17
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:51,790
When I was growing up, I never
thought our family's situation...

18
00:00:53,290 --> 00:00:55,260
was that serious.

19
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:59,130
In front of other people,
in front of that jerk Min Jun,

20
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:02,300
I held my head high
because I was your son.

21
00:01:03,770 --> 00:01:06,470
Because at least
I wasn't born out of an affair.

22
00:01:12,910 --> 00:01:14,950
When I looked at Min Jun,

23
00:01:16,150 --> 00:01:18,350
I felt superior to him.

24
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:21,250
But...

25
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:26,320
I'm the one who was born
from a filthy, improper relationship.

26
00:01:28,290 --> 00:01:29,290
It's disgusting.

27
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:31,560
You're disgusting, and so am I.

28
00:01:33,970 --> 00:01:34,970
Now...

29
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:39,140
I'm not the son of Adele Group
Chairman Park Tae Ho.

30
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:42,240
I'm the chauffeur's son.

31
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:44,310
- Hyun Jun.
- I...

32
00:01:49,110 --> 00:01:52,150
I don't want to live
as the chauffeur's son!

33
00:01:54,250 --> 00:01:56,120
Even if I'm the son of a murderer,

34
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,230
I want to live as Park Tae Ho's son.

35
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,240
This...

36
00:02:14,770 --> 00:02:15,770
This is the kind of man I am.

37
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:20,180
Now that the truth is out,

38
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,850
I realize what a disgusting,
cowardly man I am.

39
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,920
The shame is so overwhelming...

40
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:34,560
that when I try to stand,
my knees just give out.

41
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:41,070
I can't hold my head up
in front of anyone.

42
00:03:04,790 --> 00:03:05,790
Mom...

43
00:03:06,490 --> 00:03:07,490
Yes, this is she.

44
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,690
I see.

45
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,900
I'll head over there right now.

46
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,430
Sure.

47
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:28,980
Pull yourself together
and hold your head high.

48
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:31,820
No matter what anyone says,
you're Park Tae Ho's son.

49
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,920
Nothing has changed.

50
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:38,220
I'm trying to convince myself
of that too.

51
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:41,590
If it could simply be willed away,

52
00:03:41,690 --> 00:03:44,760
I'd rather close my eyes
and live in denial.

53
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,200
But...

54
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,270
But Mom, is this even right?

55
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:52,340
It's right if you want it to be.

56
00:03:54,210 --> 00:03:56,470
I'll find a way
to make it right for you,

57
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:58,640
so don't worry.

58
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:01,350
No.

59
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:05,920
No, I'll handle this myself.

60
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,150
Don't do anything reckless again...

61
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,520
claiming it's for my sake.

62
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:12,960
You can't handle this alone.

63
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:18,400
How did that witch end up
telling you about this?

64
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,800
You were aware...

65
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:23,070
of it?

66
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,140
That Choi Yu Na had found out?

67
00:04:27,370 --> 00:04:29,270
What? Choi Yu Na?

68
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,810
You didn't hear it from Choi Yu Na?

69
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:35,350
Then who else knows besides her?

70
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:37,920
Nobody, of course.

71
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:42,050
I've gotten so used to cursing
that it just slipped out.

72
00:04:43,290 --> 00:04:44,290
Anyway,

73
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:48,330
was it that piece of trash,
Choi Yu Na, who told you the secret?

74
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:50,400
I told you I'd handle it.

75
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:54,430
If you feel even the slightest bit
of shame or guilt toward me,

76
00:04:56,370 --> 00:04:57,840
then please, don't do anything.

77
00:05:07,250 --> 00:05:09,110
I bet that piece of trash
blackmailed him...

78
00:05:09,710 --> 00:05:11,380
and got on his nerves.

79
00:05:14,850 --> 00:05:16,750
I have to be the one to shut her up.

80
00:05:22,290 --> 00:05:24,100
It's nice
that we're all together again.

81
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:26,800
Woo Jin told me...

82
00:05:27,130 --> 00:05:28,900
you discussed Eunhwa Trading.

83
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,670
Yes, about Park Cheol Su.

84
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,600
I couldn't find him with just a name
and phone number.

85
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:38,410
We thought we could track him down
if he secured bomb materials...

86
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:41,280
through Eunhwa Trading.

87
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:44,080
Asking Eunhwa Trading
about Park Cheol Su's whereabouts...

88
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:45,150
could be risky.

89
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,020
They've done business
with Park Tae Ho for a long time,

90
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:50,090
so word that we're looking
for Park Cheol Su...

91
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:51,790
could get back to Park Tae Ho.

92
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:57,630
Then what if we try to meet
Park Cheol Su in person?

93
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,000
In person?

94
00:05:59,060 --> 00:06:02,100
We can ask Eunhwa Trading
for an explosives expert.

95
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:04,700
Right. Just like Park Tae Ho did.

96
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:08,040
So instead of chasing Park Cheol Su,
we lure him out.

97
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,510
That's a great idea. See?

98
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:12,810
When we put our heads together,
we find a way.

99
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:15,610
Then I'll go to Eunhwa Trading.

100
00:06:15,810 --> 00:06:17,450
They don't know me there,

101
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,280
so I should be able to avoid
arousing suspicion.

102
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:21,820
Then I'll handle Park Tae Ho.

103
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:25,720
Even if we find Park Cheol Su,
his testimony alone won't be enough.

104
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,390
If we find
Park Tae Ho's slush fund ledger,

105
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,060
there should be a record
of the payment...

106
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:31,530
he made to Park Cheol Su.

107
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:34,300
In the meantime,
I'll keep an eye on Oh Jung Ran.

108
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:37,170
We need to check
if she's hiding any information...

109
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:39,200
about Eunhwa Trading
or Park Cheol Su.

110
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:44,140
Coordinating like this
really makes us feel like a team.

111
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,840
Maybe we should toast to that.

112
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:49,710
Go, team.

113
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,490
What are you smiling about?

114
00:07:00,930 --> 00:07:03,960
I keep thinking
about Woo Jin calling us a team.

115
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:07,060
Not long ago,

116
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:10,540
we saw each other
as obstacles to our revenge.

117
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,270
But now,

118
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:17,010
I'm glad we're now in a position
to help each other.

119
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:20,010
I'm glad, too.

120
00:07:22,850 --> 00:07:23,850
From now on,

121
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:27,220
I hope we won't have
any reason to fight.

122
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:34,290
Are you worried we'll end up
fighting over Adele Group?

123
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:41,530
I've thought a lot about
why you married Hyun Jun.

124
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:44,400
You want Adele Group, don't you?

125
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,440
Yes.

126
00:07:49,410 --> 00:07:52,180
If I can't take
Chairman Park's life,

127
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:54,150
I wanted to at least
take away Adele...

128
00:07:54,210 --> 00:07:56,180
which he cherishes
as much as life itself.

129
00:07:58,050 --> 00:08:01,820
You believe Adele rightfully belongs
to Min Jun, don't you?

130
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,720
I do.

131
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:08,630
It's the reason
I endured 30 years at Adele.

132
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,730
However...

133
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:21,240
We won't ever fight over Adele.

134
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:26,610
I intend to respect whatever choice
you and Min Jun make.

135
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:30,280
Are you sure...

136
00:08:31,450 --> 00:08:33,990
you're okay
with your 30-year-long plan...

137
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:36,220
falling apart because of me?

138
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:42,030
You might not be able to get
your revenge on Oh Jung Ran.

139
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,730
I highly doubt that.

140
00:08:44,430 --> 00:08:48,500
I'll find a way for us
to get our revenge together.

141
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:05,450
Why did you want to see me?

142
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:09,390
What did you do to Hyun Jun?

143
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:13,790
What did you do to make him call off
the legal team's actions?

144
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:17,760
Really? Did Hyun Jun tell
the legal team to stand down?

145
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:20,970
Shouldn't you be questioning him...

146
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:23,130
instead of dragging me here
to grill me?

147
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,140
Why are you taking it out on me?

148
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,240
Is that what you think?

149
00:09:27,310 --> 00:09:29,040
Haven't I been caught
in the middle...

150
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,470
of a feud between brothers?

151
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:34,450
You're still hitting on Chloe,

152
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:36,250
so maybe...

153
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:38,880
Hyun Jun decided to interfere
with everything you do...

154
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:42,750
and is taking it too far
just to show you up.

155
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:46,060
Forget it. I didn't expect
an honest answer from you anyway.

156
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:48,290
If you somehow thought...

157
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:52,360
you could stop me by using Hyun Jun,

158
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,630
you're mistaken.

159
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:57,540
The legal team will follow my orders
since I'm the vice president,

160
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:00,770
and we'll proceed
with the legal action.

161
00:10:08,210 --> 00:10:10,280
Park Hyun Jun alone isn't enough
to stop this?

162
00:10:11,780 --> 00:10:14,420
Now that Min Jun is being recognized
as the successor,

163
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,490
Hyun Jun is no match for him.

164
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:21,530
Then does that mean
I have to take Min Jun down?

165
00:10:27,830 --> 00:10:29,430
(Ms. Oh Jung Ran)

166
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:43,280
Tell me right now.
How did you find out about Hyun Jun?

167
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:47,150
How else?
I ran a DNA test, obviously.

168
00:10:47,990 --> 00:10:51,420
Driver Song made it way too obvious.

169
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,420
So?

170
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:55,930
What are you planning to do,
holding Hyun Jun's secret over us?

171
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:58,530
By blackmailing you
and Park Hyun Jun...

172
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,760
You threatened him?

173
00:11:00,130 --> 00:11:01,230
Why you...

174
00:11:03,130 --> 00:11:05,200
I'm trying to go up against Min Jun.

175
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:11,640
You don't want to be with Min Jun,
but go up against him?

176
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:18,350
That's right.
Since he's trying to ruin my life,

177
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,620
I'm going to fight back.

178
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:23,290
I wanted him because I loved him.

179
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:25,390
But being blinded by love...

180
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:28,430
doesn't mean I'm willing
to throw my life away for it.

181
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,100
What's this new development?

182
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:35,900
I may hold Hyun Jun's secret,

183
00:11:35,970 --> 00:11:39,140
but the fact is
that we have the same goal.

184
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:42,070
Join me in fighting Min Jun...

185
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:44,840
and let's remove him
as vice president. No,

186
00:11:46,210 --> 00:11:48,650
let's take him down
as the successor.

187
00:11:52,950 --> 00:11:56,620
I'm relieved you're going
after Min Jun and not my Hyun Jun,

188
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,520
but let's get one thing straight.

189
00:11:58,890 --> 00:12:03,760
Don't think you can use this secret
to control me and my son.

190
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,630
If you cross me,

191
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,770
I can make sure you never open
that mouth of yours again.

192
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:17,270
Watch it, or Park Hyun Jun
will become Song Hyun Jun.

193
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:19,440
- Hey!
- That's why...

194
00:12:19,710 --> 00:12:23,850
you'll just have to tolerate me
ordering you around.

195
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:27,520
You'd better find a way to remove Min Jun
from his position...

196
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:29,020
as vice president.

197
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:40,800
I don't think
she'll run her mouth for now,

198
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:42,830
but this is going to be a pain.

199
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:48,470
Park Tae Ho, Kim Myung Hui,
Park Min Jun, and now Choi Yu Na.

200
00:12:48,540 --> 00:12:49,740
I'm surrounded by enemies.

201
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:54,040
How can I have no allies
and only enemies?

202
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:55,780
Darn it.

203
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,300
Why are you here?

204
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,870
Did you meet with Oh Jung Ran?

205
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:22,170
I came to see Min Jun,
but I wasn't able to,

206
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,180
so I just stopped by on my way out.

207
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:27,310
I heard she got out of the basement,

208
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:29,010
so I thought
I should at least say hello.

209
00:13:29,650 --> 00:13:30,810
I didn't know...

210
00:13:30,810 --> 00:13:33,150
you and my mother-in-law
were that close.

211
00:13:35,950 --> 00:13:37,250
And what about you two?

212
00:13:37,350 --> 00:13:39,390
Have you gotten close enough...

213
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:41,390
to start coming home
from work together?

214
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:48,230
I've been trying hard
to get along with her.

215
00:13:49,170 --> 00:13:52,070
I heard we were pretty close
before I lost my memory...

216
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:54,640
but now she won't give me an inch.

217
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:56,610
Why bother trying
to get close to her?

218
00:13:57,470 --> 00:13:59,340
She just uses people
when it's convenient for her...

219
00:13:59,810 --> 00:14:01,650
and then tosses them aside.

220
00:14:02,110 --> 00:14:06,180
The problem isn't me.
It's you, Ms. Choi.

221
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:08,690
You're not someone
worth keeping around,

222
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,720
nor are you trustworthy.

223
00:14:20,330 --> 00:14:23,630
I'll ask Oh Jung Ran
what Choi Yu Na was doing here.

224
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,640
Okay.

225
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:28,770
We should keep our distance
from now on, even at home.

226
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:31,510
Sure. You go on ahead.

227
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:50,260
I just saw Ms. Choi leaving.
What was that about?

228
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:52,760
Well...

229
00:14:53,100 --> 00:14:55,570
We were just talking.

230
00:14:55,970 --> 00:14:57,000
About what?

231
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,700
Do I have to report everything
to you?

232
00:15:00,970 --> 00:15:02,070
Stop sticking your nose
in my business.

233
00:15:02,070 --> 00:15:03,970
Just hurry up
and find Park Cheol Su.

234
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:05,580
Did you find anything?

235
00:15:06,110 --> 00:15:10,550
Not yet. Like you said,
he's a very secretive person.

236
00:15:11,020 --> 00:15:13,280
Just how long
do you expect me to wait?

237
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:15,350
Do you have any idea
what I went through all day...

238
00:15:15,350 --> 00:15:16,550
because of Kim Myung Hui?

239
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:20,360
I swear, I can't get
a single day of peace. Not one.

240
00:15:28,330 --> 00:15:30,670
She's definitely hiding something.

241
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:34,440
Learning more about Park Cheol Su
and Eunhwa Trading is one thing,

242
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:38,910
but I also need to figure out
what Yu Na is up to.

243
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:45,650
Goodness.

244
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:50,690
Are you still in a lot of pain?

245
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:53,420
Here.

246
00:15:54,090 --> 00:15:56,060
This is a tonic to help you recover.

247
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:07,040
What on earth? Why is it so bitter?

248
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:11,410
The medicine that's good for you
is always bitter.

249
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:21,390
I can't believe all the trouble
Oh Jung Ran is causing me.

250
00:16:23,950 --> 00:16:26,260
If it weren't for you, Myung Hui,

251
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:29,460
I'd still be lying in bed.

252
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:33,360
So,

253
00:16:35,370 --> 00:16:39,240
never let Oh Jung Ran fool you
into doubting me again.

254
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:42,440
I already apologized for that...

255
00:16:43,310 --> 00:16:45,240
and even said we should make
our marriage official.

256
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,640
Right.

257
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:50,380
Just as you said,
we'll register our marriage...

258
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:52,250
and become a legally married couple.

259
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:55,420
But as a wedding gift,

260
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:57,390
show me how you truly feel.

261
00:16:57,790 --> 00:17:02,230
I want to see for myself
if you truly trust me, sir.

262
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:04,230
It sounds like...

263
00:17:05,860 --> 00:17:07,900
you want something.

264
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:13,970
Let me manage the slush fund.

265
00:17:16,370 --> 00:17:17,640
The slush fund?

266
00:17:19,010 --> 00:17:21,450
If I take over
Oh Jung Ran's responsibilities,

267
00:17:22,080 --> 00:17:24,650
I'll know our marriage is real,

268
00:17:25,250 --> 00:17:28,520
that you trust me more than her,

269
00:17:29,420 --> 00:17:31,290
and it'll put my mind at ease.

270
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:46,570
So,

271
00:17:46,970 --> 00:17:49,510
how are things going
with the slush fund?

272
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:54,480
We haven't been able to do anything
since you collapsed, sir.

273
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:57,180
The gallery is practically
shut down as well.

274
00:17:57,180 --> 00:17:58,650
The police, the media,

275
00:17:59,550 --> 00:18:00,950
and even the politicians.

276
00:18:02,050 --> 00:18:04,960
- Are you managing them?
- That's been put on hold as well.

277
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:09,960
They all understand,
given your health issues,

278
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,930
but if the money stops flowing,

279
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,800
those relationships will start
to fall apart.

280
00:18:14,530 --> 00:18:16,630
Yes, of course.

281
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:21,640
I suppose we need someone
to oversee the slush fund.

282
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:23,840
Are you thinking of putting
President Kim in charge?

283
00:18:36,850 --> 00:18:37,890
Guys.

284
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:40,760
Are you sure about this?

285
00:18:42,130 --> 00:18:43,730
Don't worry.

286
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:52,700
Just think of it as a special kind
of business meeting.

287
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:56,170
I hope you've got
the whole plan down.

288
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:59,940
A certain assemblyman,
whose identity we can't reveal,

289
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:03,510
ordered us to find
an explosives expert.

290
00:19:04,650 --> 00:19:05,650
Don't mess this up.

291
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:08,250
Just focus on your part.
Unbelievable.

292
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:10,790
Don't wait here. Go to the cafe.

293
00:19:10,890 --> 00:19:13,120
Got it. Be careful.

294
00:19:16,390 --> 00:19:17,760
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

295
00:19:49,630 --> 00:19:51,460
Why did you want to come here?

296
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:57,230
You said you wanted
to manage the slush fund.

297
00:19:57,530 --> 00:20:00,900
Then you should know
where the ledger is.

298
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,240
So you mean...

299
00:20:03,470 --> 00:20:07,540
Yes. That's where I keep
the slush fund ledger.

300
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:09,610
Once we've registered
our marriage...

301
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,480
and we're legally husband and wife,

302
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:14,620
I'll give you the key.

303
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:18,760
You still don't trust me, do you?

304
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:23,190
You don't trust me enough
to give me the key and the ledger.

305
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:27,000
I'm suggesting we do things
in the right order.

306
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:32,670
After we register our marriage
and you are completely mine,

307
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:37,640
I'll give it to you. So don't worry.

308
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:41,180
Oh, right. One more thing.

309
00:20:44,110 --> 00:20:45,420
This...

310
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:50,490
is a gift to symbolize our promise.
Give me your arm.

311
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:54,320
Let's see.

312
00:20:57,260 --> 00:21:00,000
It looks good on you, doesn't it?

313
00:21:01,470 --> 00:21:04,670
Make sure you keep it on.

314
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,300
Thank you, sir.

315
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:16,850
We set the bait...

316
00:21:16,850 --> 00:21:19,920
by telling Eunhwa Trading
we need an explosives expert.

317
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:22,590
Now we just have to wait
for them to take it.

318
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:27,060
But is Park Cheol Su
their only explosives expert?

319
00:21:27,060 --> 00:21:30,230
I fished for information about it
and got confirmation.

320
00:21:30,290 --> 00:21:33,330
I left my number,
so let's just wait and see.

321
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:34,970
Do you think they'll call?

322
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:38,270
I told them it was urgent
and offered to double their fee,

323
00:21:38,570 --> 00:21:40,000
so they'll definitely call.

324
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:42,540
At Eunhwa Trading,

325
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:45,240
you casually put down a huge amount
as a down payment.

326
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:47,840
Color me impressed.

327
00:21:49,180 --> 00:21:52,550
I may lack other things,
but not this.

328
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:55,320
I have to admit, I like that.

329
00:21:55,890 --> 00:21:57,750
You guys did great.

330
00:21:58,060 --> 00:21:59,460
We sure did.

331
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:03,360
(Bongmyeong Neighborhood Coffee)

332
00:22:03,460 --> 00:22:04,460
What?

333
00:22:10,770 --> 00:22:14,670
The intel team said they sent you
a listening device. Is that it?

334
00:22:15,010 --> 00:22:17,670
Yes, I got it
while I was waiting for you two.

335
00:22:17,770 --> 00:22:20,140
I figured I'd need it
to keep an eye on Oh Jung Ran.

336
00:22:28,750 --> 00:22:31,820
When did you two get so close?

337
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:35,630
Come on. Who says we're close?

338
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:38,900
You're even wearing
matching outfits and sunglasses.

339
00:22:39,130 --> 00:22:43,230
I prefer it when you two fight
rather than act all friendly.

340
00:22:43,230 --> 00:22:47,240
What? Why would you rather we fight?

341
00:22:47,300 --> 00:22:48,510
It's more fun.

342
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:52,380
Anyway, this is a bummer.

343
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:56,680
Well, I'll be going now.

344
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:02,590
Seriously?

345
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:13,960
Hyun Jun.

346
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:16,430
(Division 2 Director's Office)

347
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:20,940
What do you want?

348
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,270
(Vice President's Office)

349
00:23:22,340 --> 00:23:24,210
I came to give you this.

350
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:26,680
It's raisin tree tea.
It's good for hangovers.

351
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:30,710
You drank way too much last time.

352
00:23:31,850 --> 00:23:35,150
I brewed it all night,
so make sure you drink it.

353
00:23:36,990 --> 00:23:38,120
I'm good.

354
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:40,560
Just stay away from me.

355
00:23:55,210 --> 00:23:56,540
Didn't you hear me?

356
00:23:57,310 --> 00:23:59,140
How dare you come in here?

357
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:03,480
I'll just leave this and go.

358
00:24:03,950 --> 00:24:07,280
I made it for you, so just drink it.

359
00:24:08,990 --> 00:24:11,420
Who are you to worry about me?
What is this?

360
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:14,830
Are you showing up now to claim me
as your son and take all the credit?

361
00:24:14,890 --> 00:24:17,230
Of course not. How could I...

362
00:24:17,330 --> 00:24:18,630
Then...

363
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:23,330
don't ever show your face
in front of me again, because...

364
00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:26,800
I'm Chairman Park Tae Ho's son.

365
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:29,640
That's who I've decided to be!

366
00:24:31,910 --> 00:24:34,640
So stop showing up out of nowhere
and driving me crazy.

367
00:24:38,050 --> 00:24:40,620
But Hyun Jun...

368
00:24:41,620 --> 00:24:42,920
Hyun Jun...

369
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:59,840
Goodness.
Aren't you Hyun Jun's father?

370
00:25:00,670 --> 00:25:01,670
Excuse me?

371
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:03,710
What are you talking about?

372
00:25:03,810 --> 00:25:04,880
Come on.

373
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:09,880
You don't have to pretend in front
of me. I already know everything.

374
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:11,920
Don't tell me...

375
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:15,050
the person who told Hyun Jun was...

376
00:25:15,050 --> 00:25:17,390
Yes, that's right.

377
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:20,420
I told Hyun Jun who his father is.

378
00:25:23,390 --> 00:25:25,960
Thanks to that, Hyun Jun and Ms. Oh,

379
00:25:26,800 --> 00:25:30,300
or should I say, Jung Ran,
are now in the palm of my hand.

380
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:34,970
Now they'll both do as I say,
so you'll have...

381
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:38,210
to follow my orders too.

382
00:25:44,850 --> 00:25:46,280
What do you think you're doing?

383
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,550
You dared...

384
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:51,220
to break Hyun Jun's heart?

385
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:54,760
I may have nothing,
and I may be powerless,

386
00:25:55,130 --> 00:25:57,090
but I won't just stand by
and let you hurt my child.

387
00:25:58,230 --> 00:25:59,230
You.

388
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,770
I'll be keeping an eye on you,

389
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:04,200
so watch yourself.

390
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:13,740
Is he out of his mind?

391
00:26:14,740 --> 00:26:17,350
What about the mess he'll be in
if I expose the secret?

392
00:26:23,450 --> 00:26:24,450
Just you wait.

393
00:26:25,090 --> 00:26:29,490
Next time, I'll make you kneel
and beg me for forgiveness.

394
00:26:38,670 --> 00:26:39,670
Driver Song.

395
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:42,840
Hold on.

396
00:26:43,510 --> 00:26:45,810
Driver Song!

397
00:26:46,540 --> 00:26:47,540
Stop right there!

398
00:26:57,220 --> 00:26:58,250
Darn it.

399
00:27:10,870 --> 00:27:12,140
Don't worry.

400
00:27:12,670 --> 00:27:15,070
I'll help you get away safely.

401
00:27:15,540 --> 00:27:17,340
Why are you helping me?

402
00:27:17,340 --> 00:27:18,340
In return,

403
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:20,510
just be honest with me.

404
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:24,250
There seemed to be a commotion
in Hyun Jun's office.

405
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:27,920
Something's going on between
him and Yu Na, right?

406
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:31,420
That's...

407
00:27:31,490 --> 00:27:34,960
Is he being blackmailed by Yu Na?

408
00:27:35,890 --> 00:27:37,030
Is she threatening to expose...

409
00:27:38,530 --> 00:27:39,630
that you're his father?

410
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:45,400
I found out when my mother did.

411
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:49,240
But I have no intention
of exploiting his secret.

412
00:27:50,210 --> 00:27:54,180
If Yu Na is blackmailing
Hyun Jun with it,

413
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:55,350
please tell me.

414
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:58,110
I'll deal with her myself.

415
00:28:02,950 --> 00:28:05,690
Please help my Hyun Jun.

416
00:28:07,420 --> 00:28:09,160
So it was her all along.

417
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:10,960
She said it herself.

418
00:28:12,630 --> 00:28:14,730
Hyun Jun and even Jung Ran...

419
00:28:15,300 --> 00:28:17,630
are now doing
whatever she tells them to do.

420
00:28:19,770 --> 00:28:21,810
We need to do something about it.

421
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:25,980
Of course. I'll handle Choi Yu Na.

422
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:30,950
Just don't tell Hyun Jun
that I know about this.

423
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:32,380
Sure.

424
00:28:33,520 --> 00:28:36,190
Let me know
if there's anything I can do.

425
00:28:36,690 --> 00:28:39,860
I'll do everything I can,
even if it seems impossible.

426
00:28:40,690 --> 00:28:41,690
Just...

427
00:28:42,730 --> 00:28:43,760
say the word.

428
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:56,770
Take down Park Min Jun
from his VP position?

429
00:28:57,710 --> 00:28:58,710
No.

430
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:01,910
I shouldn't play
into Ms. Choi's hands.

431
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:03,380
I need to go after Park Tae Ho.

432
00:29:04,650 --> 00:29:07,950
It'll be game over
once Chloe finds Park Cheol Su.

433
00:29:09,850 --> 00:29:11,020
Oh Jung Ran.

434
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:14,390
Is this what you call cleaning?

435
00:29:14,690 --> 00:29:16,190
Have you never cleaned
a floor before?

436
00:29:16,990 --> 00:29:18,930
I shouldn't just do as I'm told.

437
00:29:19,760 --> 00:29:21,100
I have to find a way to save myself.

438
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:24,570
Are you refusing to do
what you're told?

439
00:29:24,930 --> 00:29:28,100
I'm going straight to the chairman
and Ms. Kim with this.

440
00:29:28,270 --> 00:29:31,510
Hold on. Why are you misinterpreting
what I said?

441
00:29:32,140 --> 00:29:33,940
I didn't mean
I wouldn't follow your orders.

442
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:36,080
It's someone else's orders that...

443
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:54,030
You're here an awful lot.

444
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:55,700
Are you a debt collector?

445
00:29:56,570 --> 00:29:59,540
I told you to call me,
but you never did.

446
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:02,870
Have you still not figured out
how to take down Park Min Jun?

447
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,910
It hasn't even been a day yet.

448
00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:10,150
How do you expect me to come up
with a plan overnight?

449
00:30:10,410 --> 00:30:12,650
Time isn't a luxury you have.

450
00:30:15,690 --> 00:30:16,850
Hyun Jun.

451
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:20,490
You met with Choi Yu Na anyway?

452
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:24,090
I told you I'd handle it
and not to meet her.

453
00:30:27,530 --> 00:30:28,530
Are you kidding me?

454
00:30:28,930 --> 00:30:30,400
Now you're blackmailing
my mother too?

455
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:32,100
Stop it.

456
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:35,970
Ms. Choi, come back later, okay?

457
00:30:49,490 --> 00:30:52,320
For two people at my mercy,

458
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:55,530
you're awfully loud.

459
00:30:56,130 --> 00:30:59,100
Ms. Oh... or should I call you
Hyun Jun's mother?

460
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:02,470
Go get me a glass of cold water.

461
00:31:02,730 --> 00:31:04,170
- Hey.
- Or maybe...

462
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,870
I should tell the chairman.

463
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:08,240
- You little...
- Don't.

464
00:31:08,910 --> 00:31:09,910
Drop it.

465
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:12,380
Getting a glass of water
isn't a big deal.

466
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:13,980
Just a second.

467
00:31:24,020 --> 00:31:25,020
Happy now?

468
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:29,460
See?

469
00:31:30,190 --> 00:31:32,100
I'm the one in charge here.

470
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:35,160
Did you say I was blackmailing her?

471
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:40,770
Do you have any idea how much
I'm letting you get away with?

472
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:45,240
Since you couldn't handle Min Jun,
I gave your mother a chance.

473
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,610
And since...

474
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:49,950
she can't even leave the house,
I came here myself.

475
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:51,950
And then there's Driver Song...

476
00:31:54,820 --> 00:31:56,020
Your father...

477
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:59,360
threw a fit
and even flung his tea at me.

478
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:03,890
You should've seen him
trying to act like a dad.

479
00:32:03,930 --> 00:32:05,400
Who are you calling my dad?

480
00:32:23,250 --> 00:32:26,650
Hyun Jun's not Park Tae Ho's son,

481
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:29,250
but Driver Song's son?

482
00:32:57,880 --> 00:33:00,780
(Pearl in Red)

483
00:33:00,780 --> 00:33:03,920
He may be Park Tae Ho's son,
but he's your son too.

484
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:05,590
Do whatever it takes to protect him.

485
00:33:06,090 --> 00:33:08,560
He's my son. Of course I will.

486
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:12,100
I was making him pay
for what Driver Song did to me.

487
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:14,130
Think of it as taking a hit
for your father.

488
00:33:14,130 --> 00:33:16,770
What's this?
What is this doing here?

489
00:33:16,870 --> 00:33:18,570
Did Kim Myung Hui...

490
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:21,040
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
